### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7101
@productId = {{createProduct.response.body.id}}

### 1. Create Product with Image and Price
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Products
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Title"

محصول نمونه با تصویر و قیمت
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

این محصول دارای تصویر و قیمت است
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Price"

250000
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="IsActive"

true
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CategoryId"

{{$guid}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ImageFile"; filename="product-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/sample-product.jpg
--WebAppBoundary--

